-- Azerbaijan’s Capital Baku Bids for 2020 Summer Olympic Games
-- B y   Z u l f u g a r   A g a y e v
-- 2012-02-15T06:46:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-15/azerbaijan-s-capital-baku-bids-for-2020-summer-olympic-games.html
The capital of the oil-rich former
Soviet republic of  Azerbaijan , Baku, formally bid for the 2020
Olympics.  The International Olympics Committee has already received
Baku’s application, the Azeri organizing committee for the 2020
Olympics said on its Twitter Inc. account yesterday.  Baku will play host to the Eurovision song contest this
year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zulfugar Agayev in Baku at 
 zagayev@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
